lead_paragraph: Pleased as Kentucky coach John Calipari was by last week's performance on the national stage, he seemed more encouraged by the second-ranked Wildcats' encore that figures to raise their profile even more.

headline.print_headline: No. 2 Kentucky Has No Trouble With Duquesne in 93-59 Rout
